data.description: Fantastic award winning, Jenks Southeast Grade School !! Choice Interior Lot with trees on a short street. Great Woodfield neighborhood with a terrific community environment ! Super Quality plan with 4 Bedrooms featuring 2 suites down and 2 up. Fabulous 2 story entry with distinctive Stairway & overlook.Large Vaulted Living room can make a great office. Big Formal Dining plus a breakfast nook that opens up to a large Granite Counter Kitchen & a generous family room with a distinctive Fireplace. The 1st floor Primary Suite features a sitting area, private back yard door and a full luxury Bath; plus a generous walk in closet. Guest Bedroom suite down with pullman bath. Very large gameroom up, with 2 Bedrooms and a pullman bath. Wonderful Access to Tulsa, Bixby and Jenks; Entertainment, dining, shopping, medical, City & County parks all within a 5 mile radius. Super Value on Price per Square foot - A Must see!!
